videos.description: Saint Mary's Calvin Hermanson knocks down the wide-open corner 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Calvin Hermanson makes shooting look easy

videos.description: Utah's Sedrick Barefield finds Donnie Tillman, who drives from the baseline and finishes with the two-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Donnie Tillman with the easy dunk

videos.description: Utah's David Collette uses the slip screen to get to the rim and finish with the dunk.
videos.headline: David Collette 'brings the pain' with the slam

videos.description: Saint Mary's Tanner Krebs lays it in in the final seconds of the 2nd quarter to even the score against Utah.
videos.headline: Tanner Krebs ties it going to halftime

videos.description: Saint Mary's Jock Landale shows why he won WCC player of the year, as he gets by the defender for the dunk.
videos.headline: Jock Landale with the two-handed jam

videos.description: Utah's Tyler Rawson hits the three from the wing to stay competitive with Saint Mary's in the NIT Quarterfinals
videos.headline: Rawson nails clutch 3-pointer for Utah

videos.description: Utah's Sedrick Barefield surges the Utes' offense with consecutive 3-pointers in overtime against Saint Mary's.
videos.headline: Barefield hits back-to-back 3s for Utes
